publicwhip.spmotion: *S2M-5319 Ms Wendy Alexander on behalf of the Finance Committee: Report on Stage 2 of the 2007-08 Budget Process—That the Parliament notes the 9th Report, 2006 (Session 2) of the Finance Committee, Stage 2 of the 2007-08 Budget Process (SP Paper 695) and refers the report and its recommendations to the Scottish Executive for consideration.
